data.description: Charming Cottage Style Home just five doors up from the Royal Palms of McGregor Boulevard in a Great Established Neighborhood . This two bedroom, two full bath home has the  cozy feel of vintage but updates galore with it's bright and airy rooms, lots of windows, and a private yard with a firepit for those cool evenings. This home is close to downtown Fort Myers, Fort Myers Country Club, fine dining, shopping, schools and the hospital.  Home boasts a new roof in March of 2023, new fence for the back yard, and the AC was replaced in 2017.  This is the best priced home in a wonderful neighborhood and would make a great investment property, Airbnb, seasonal or year-round home and it is flood zone X. This will not last long at this price!
